article.headline: Rice 78, Louisiana Tech 64
article.story: RUSTON, La. (AP) -- Jason McKrieth scored 25 points to help lead Rice to a 78-64 victory over Louisiana Tech on Thursday night. Morris Almond added 18 points for the Owls (17-10, 11-6 Western Athletic) on perfect 6-of-6 shooting from the field, 4-of-4 shooting from behind the arc and 2-for-2 shooting from the free-throw line. Michael Harris scored 13 points and pulled down 12 rebounds. Corey Dean led the Bulldogs (13-14, 8-9) with 24 points. Paul Millsap added a double-double of 15 points and 15 rebounds and Eric Woods finished with 10 points.
